批量安装：
pip install -i https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/ -r mypackages.txt --trusted-host https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/

单独安装：
pip install -i https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/ beautifulsoup4 --trusted-host https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/
pip install -i https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/ lxml --trusted-host https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/
pip install -i https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/ pandas --trusted-host https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/
pip install -i https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/ scrapy --trusted-host https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/
pip install -i https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/ pretty_errors --trusted-host https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/
pip install -i https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/ PyMySQL --trusted-host https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/